lenders.occupational_info:
Business Description (Step by Step):
For Partner Side:
3rd step: Partner helps to find Buyer & communicate Buyer and receive proposal and send to me.
5th Step: After Collect Design & Proposal, partner sends to buyer and collect Technical File for Sample Development and All document send to me.
7th step: After Receive “Product Sample”, “Selling Pricing sheet- for Buyer” send to buyer & price negotiate with buyer.
8th Step: After Order Confirmation, Partner Collect L/C from Buyer & Send Me.

 For Bangladeshi Side (Me & My Team):
1st step: Collect Money for Start Business, Some money spends from my team and some money spends from my Partner. (Our Business Office not required this time. Because, I did not spend extra money for business start. Initially Business office Started at my home Dhaka, Bangladesh. After Business growing ahead, then we arrange a new business office. If Partner agrees, He had done regular task in Bangladeshi Office regularly or some time. Some fund ready to available for Product Sample development.
2nd step: Collect Business Permission, Export & Import Permission from Bangladeshi Government. Others Miscellaneous Government Formalities Maintain by my team.
4th Step: If buyer Provide design then, my team develop design and proposal & Send to you.
& Sample development from factory.
Collect Technical File.
6th Step: Collect Document & “Sample development” from factory (Required some fund for sample develop) send to partner “Product Sample”, “Actual Cost sheet of product-for partner” & “Selling Pricing sheet- for Buyer”.
9th Step: After Received Export L/C (Selling Price), open a New L/C “Cost Price” in Bangladesh and submit to Factory for production. (Note: Required Fund for L/C Open.)
10th step: Follow up with planning/production/commercial work & ensure shipment move on time. Follow up with commercial on correct shipping documents, shipment advice and payment. Co-ordinate with buyer, accessories supplier, factory management, planning & commercial for on time shipment. Maintains all relevant merchandising communication, order files, reports etc. required for processing orders efficiently. Collect L/C Value from Bank, Send Profit to Partner (As per Agreement). 

Note: This Step Not Hard, It’s so easy Task. My Team fully Support to Every Task.
If Product design needed. I & My Team Help for Design. But, Product Design Always Provide By “Buyer”
All Communication Support Provide Me & My Team (If you want),
 All Processing Task Provide Me & My Team (If you want).
